  "body": "---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nCan't instantiate a truffle \"contract abstraction\" object with only the address and the ABI of a contract.\r\nA  truffle generated build `.json` file is required.\r\n\r\nI am using an extra truffle setup to deal with the deployment of a contract that is on a different solidity version than the rest of my project (e.g. dai token on solidity 5).\r\n\r\nHaving these instance will allow to make more robust migration scripts and facilitate testing. \r\nShort discussion @ https://gitter.im/ConsenSys/truffle?at=6008714e2cb18a437c2e8721",
